quran[19{c,v,t}:
26,1,toy seen meem
26,2,yeh kitaab Mubin ki ayaat hain
26,3,"ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, shayad tum is gham mein apni jaan kho do ge ke yeh log imaan nahi laatay"
26,4,hum chahain to aasman se aisi nishani nazil kar satke hain ke inn ki gardanein is ke agay jhuk jayen
26,5,inn logon ke paas Rehman ki taraf se jo nai nasiyaat bhi aati hai yeh is se mun mourr letay hain
26,6,"ab ke yeh jhutla chuke hain, anqareeb inn ko is cheez ki haqeeqat ( mukhtalif tareeqon se ) maloom ho jaye gi jis ka yeh mazaq uratay rahay hain"
26,7,aur kya unhon ne kabhi zameen par nigah nahi daali ke hum ne kitni kaseer miqdaar mein har terhan ki umdah nabataat is mein peda ki hain ?
26,8,"yaqeenan is mein aik nishani hai, magar un mein se aksar maan-ne walay nahi"
26,9,aur haqeeqat yeh hai ke tera rab zabardast bhi hai aur Raheem bhi
26,10,"aِnhin is waqt ka qissa sunaaoo jab ke tumahray rab ne moose ko puraka"" zalim qoum ke paas ja"
26,11,"firaon ki qoum ke paas, kya woh drtay nahi? """
26,12,"uss ne arz kya"" ae rab, mujhe khauf hai ke woh mujhe jhutla den ge"
26,13,mera seenah ghat-ta hai aur meri zabaan nahi chalti aap haroon ki taraf risalat bhejen
26,14,"aur mujh par unn ke haan aik jurm ka ilzaam bhi hai, is liye darta hon ke woh mujhe qatal kar den ge """
26,15,"farmaya"" hargiz nahi, tum dono jao hamari nishanain le kar, hum tumahray sath sab kuch suntay rahen ge"
26,16,"firaon ke paas jao aur is se kaho, hum ko Rab-ul-Aa'lmeen ne is liye bheja hai"
26,17,"ke to bani Israel ko hamaray sath jaane day """
26,18,"firaon ne kaha"" kya hum ne tujh ko apne haan bacha sa nahi paala tha? to ne apni Umar ke kayi saal hamaray haan guzaray"
26,19,"aur is ke baad kar gaya jo kuch ke kar gaya, to bara ahsaan faramosh aadmi hai """
